    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Now let’s re-write exactly the same equation, but using a bunch of machine learning math jargon (that you can ignore for now):</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-9">
                <div class="image-wrapper"><div class="image_style" style="width:96%;"><picture><source sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 1400w" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" srcset="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/1*ZyboMOVQ5zOv0ZTC4a3usA.png 